node.text: @justasknora Hear hear, Nora! 🙌🏻 Have a fabbbbb day ahead! ✨
TEXT US BEAUTY 😍🔥

👗 All dressed up, but nowhere to go 🤷🏻‍♀️⠀
.⠀
Last day of the circuit breaker, but honestly, nothing much is gonna change on my side 🧘🏻 We’ve been dutifully staying at home, stepping out to the supermarket once a week at max 🛒 I haven’t been on any transportation, be it MRT, bus or a cab in two months 🚌🚉🚖⠀
.⠀
The big plus is I’ll get to see my parents soon! 👯‍♀️ I used to see them at least twice a week, so I’m anticipating a big feast when we reunite this weekend!🍴⠀
.⠀
I'm probably not dressing like this to go to their place though, so my pretty dresses will still be staying home 🏡⠀
.⠀
What's the first non-CB thing you're gonna do when the gates open slightly from tomorrow? ⛩😷🍃

.⁠⠀
.⁠⠀
.⠀
#CircuitBreaker #CircuitBreakerSG #SGCircuitBreaker #CBLife #StayHomeforSG #StayHomeforSGChallenge #SGUnited #StayAtHomeSG #OOTD #OOTDSG
@patfancygirl I have to admit, our Zoom meeting triggered a wave of "I want to wear this gownnnn" in me over the weekend and I took them out for a spin! 😆
You have to wear that outfit at our next Zoom meeting!

@fj.mama Hee, shops are still closed though, which I reckon is a good idea, based on the patterns of second waves in other countries. Then again, you just made me realised that parks should be open now? 🌿
Tmr can go out liao!!! Lol 😆
@jenkedrie You're most kind, Jen! Things we get up to when at home! 😝
You look gorgeous and adorable at the same time!
@happy.pin.shop I'm still staying in! How about you guys?
#stayhomesg 🇸🇬
@agmiletic TOTALLY, Ag! I wore makeup and a dress 2 weeks ago and I felt totally different, especially after I put on eyelashes! 😝
@positiveleepeilin i got all dressed up for Mother’s Day to go to my dining room and really does make one feel better i must say 🤗
@agmiletic Heehee, that’s a fab destination, Ag! 💁🏻‍♀️ Now to plan a glamorous visit to the living room 💃🏻
Love the dress♥️ and we need to dress up a few times in this quarantine to make our souls feel better♥️
Love it!! Things have been opening up around here.. going out to eat has new meaning ☺️
This dress is everything!! Also yesterday we went out for a meal and i wore high heels i had bought during this time. I couldnt not wear them!!

@genevievefunsizeloh Hi Gen, it’s from @nissa_official I believe it’s a Romanian family owned business ✨ Thanks for the encouragement! Heehee, I’m seeing so much different types of creativity during this period! 😍
i absolutely love love love your dress! where did you get it from? keep your chin up and keep doing the awesome storytelling and instagram pics!

@justasknora That sounds so romantic somehow, Nora! Over a bridge 🌉 Totally with you on worrying about their safety... I’m still wondering if I should keep my mask on when with them. Hearts received, Nora! ✨😘✨
Yes the 😷 on or off with family is always a question to think of @positiveleepeilin I don’t have the answer for you but I wish you the BEST visit with them ♥️ family is everything in my view!!!
@justasknora Hear hear, Nora! 🙌🏻 Have a fabbbbb day ahead! ✨

So happy to hear you can see your parents soon @positiveleepeilin 🙏 mine live 10 minutes by 🚙 over a bridge away but it’s been challenging seeing them these days. I worry about their safety. Excited for big hugs and a delicious meal 🥘 with them as well! Sending you 💖 today!!!
@giorgianniphotography Heehee, had to take a whirl in the kitchen in this! 💃🏻😝 I highly recommend this exercise, Giorgianni!
This dress 😍😍😍 How wonderful you will be able to see your parents soon, I can’t imagine not seeing mine weekly!
@jojollyna I’m a hugger, so I miss that so much, Alina! I miss my 1+ year old niece the most... gonna be a long while till I see her 😢
So exciting you can see your parents! I miss to do so many things, but the most of all I wish I could hug my parents 😰🥰
@stephaniedgant Thank you, Stephanie! ✨😘 the bunny ears help! 🐰
Well you sure look adorable.
